<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Listen, my people, for I will warn you,</para>

<para style="q1">Israel, if you would only listen to me!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />There must be no foreign god among you;</para>

<para style="q1">you must not worship any foreign god.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />I am Yahweh your God,</para>

<para style="q1">who brought you out of the land of Egypt.</para>

<para style="q1">Open your mouth wide, and I will fill it.</para>
